32 TRIAL LASTING MORE THAN 14 DAYS, THE NOTICE REQUIRED UNDER PARAGRAPH
33 (1) OF THIS SUBSECTION SHALL BE PROVIDED NOT LESS THAN 3 DAYS AND NOT

